<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

  <GeneDef ParentName="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneHivemind_Sync">
	<defName>WVC_HiveMind_Thoughts</defName>
	<label>shared thoughts</label>
	<description>Carriers of this gene have a psychic connection with other carriers. Due to which they share some of their thoughts.</description>
	<geneClass>WVC_XenotypesAndGenes.Gene_HiveMind_Thoughts</geneClass>
	<iconPath>WVC/UI/Genes3/Gene_HiveMind_Thoughts</iconPath>
	<displayOrderInCategory>20</displayOrderInCategory>
	<biostatCpx>2</biostatCpx>
	<biostatArc>2</biostatArc>
	<biostatMet>-2</biostatMet>
	<customEffectDescriptions>
		<li>Every day or when a new mind is added, it synchronizes the &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;memories&lt;/color&gt;.</li>
		<li>Only &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;temporary memories&lt;/color&gt; are synchronized, permanent ones are not affected.</li>
		<li>Synchronizes to the &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;higher&lt;/color&gt; value.</li>
		<!-- <li>Allows to change the ideology of the entire mind to any desired one, at any time.</li> -->
	</customEffectDescriptions>
  </GeneDef>

  <!-- ============================ -->

  <GeneDef ParentName="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneHivemind_Sync">
	<defName>WVC_HiveMind_Opinion</defName>
	<label>shared opinion</label>
	<description>Carriers of this gene have a psychic connection with other carriers. Thanks to this, they have a much better opinion of each other.</description>
	<geneClass>WVC_XenotypesAndGenes.Gene_HiveMind_Opinion</geneClass>
	<iconPath>WVC/UI/Genes3/Gene_HiveMind_Opinion</iconPath>
	<displayOrderInCategory>50</displayOrderInCategory>
	<biostatCpx>1</biostatCpx>
	<biostatArc>2</biostatArc>
	<biostatMet>-1</biostatMet>
	<customEffectDescriptions>
		<li>Every day or when a new mind is added, the hive gets an &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;opinion offset&lt;/color&gt; lasting about a day.</li>
		<li>Affects the hive's opinion with the &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;carrier&lt;/color&gt; and the &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;carrier's opinion with the hive&lt;/color&gt;, without affecting the opinion between other pawns of the hive.</li>
	</customEffectDescriptions>
	<modExtensions>
		<li Class="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes.GeneExtension_Opinion">
			<thoughtDef>WVC_HiveMind_Opinion</thoughtDef>
		</li>
	</modExtensions>
  </GeneDef>

  <ThoughtDef ParentName="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_Thought_MemorySocial_Base">
	<defName>WVC_HiveMind_Opinion</defName>
	<stackLimitForSameOtherPawn>1</stackLimitForSameOtherPawn>
	<durationDays>1</durationDays>
	<stages>
	  <li>
		<label>same hivemind</label>
		<baseOpinionOffset>9999</baseOpinionOffset>
	  </li>
	</stages>
  </ThoughtDef>

